flowchart TD
    A[User Is on SPA Notes Page] --> B[Clicks 'New Note']
    B --> C[New Note Component Rendered No Page Reload]
    C --> D[User Enters Note Title & Content]
    D --> E[Clicks Save Button]

    E --> F[Frontend Sends POST API Request]
    F --> G[Backend Server Receives Request]
    G --> H[Validate Note Data]

    H --> I{Is Data Valid?}
    I -- Yes --> J[Save Note to Database]
    J --> K[API Success Response]
    K --> L[SPA Updates State]
    L --> M[New Note Appears in Notes List Without Reload]

    I -- No --> N[API Error Response]
    N --> O[Display Validation Error On Same Page]